  "name": "RPlog_The_Trip_to_Ord_Trasi_Part_2",
  "title": "The Valley of the Damned",
  "summary": "Pressing deeper into the Dark world of Ord Trasi, Grand Admiral Danik Kreldin's expedition -- his Mandalorian Master Sergeant Cantrell, the pilot-officer Dareus, Lieutenant Krieg, the anxious stormtrooper TK-2706, and the captive Jedi Johanna te Danaan -- is set upon by shadowy fear-feeding creatures. Against Imperial instinct, Johanna proves that calm, not grenades and blaster fire, is the only defense, and a fascinated Danik begins learning to master his own fear as the beasts lose interest and slink away. The party advances along a treacherous cliff path through a statue-flanked valley toward the temple sought by Danik's Holocron. Tensions explode when Johanna snatches the Holocron and dangles it over the chasm, forcing Danik to rescind a torture order he has issued against her son Etiel. Cantrell mediates the standoff like a parent between squabbling children, the Holocron is returned, and the uneasy column resumes its march toward the temple and the tomb of power Danik craves.",
